First, update the changelog::

        emacs debian/changelog

From the parent directory, build Debian packages using::

        dpkg-buildpackage

Check the packages with lintian::

        lintian ../*.deb

Optionally update a local Debian repository as follows::

        mv ../*.deb /var/www/debian/testing
        cd /var/www/debian/testing
        dpkg-scanpackages . /dev/null | gzip -9c > Packages.gz
